- Milestone 5 (Bonus README)

-- Emmanuel Konate 101322259 implemented a background picture for the board.

-- Feature Selected: Feature 1: Images (Background Image)

--- Description
Added a background image to the Scrabble game board. The image displays behind the tiles through the gaps and transparent squares.

--- How to Use
Run the game -> The background image loads automatically and shows behind the board.

--- Implementation (ScrabbleGUI.java)

***Changes made:**
1. Added 'backgroundImage' variable
2. Modified 'boarddPanel' to override 'paintComponent()' to draw the background
3. Added code to load 'background.png' image file.
4. Made normal squares transparent to that the background is more visible
